<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SamaritanDB Demo | Mutate Network</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/input.css">
    <style>
        .side-bar {
            background: url("img/cyber.jpeg");
        }

        .side-bar-overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.486);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="w-screen h-screen md:grid md:grid-cols-[30%_70%]">
    <!-- sidebar begins -->
    <div class="bg-black side-bar bg-center hidden md:block">
        <div class="side-bar-overlay h-full px-8 py-10 ">
            <img src="img/algorealm-05.png" class="max-w-[200px]">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:hidden block pt-6 pl-4">
        <img src="img/algorealm-04.png" class=" max-w-[150px]">
    </div>
    <!-- sidebar ends-->
    <!-- Main game starts -->
    <div class="min-h-screen md:flex md:flex-col md:pt-10 pt-4 h-full ">
        <div class="md:w-[70%] w-[90%] mx-auto flex-grow">
            <p class="font-light text-xs text-gray-400 border-b border-gray-200 py-2 mb-4">
                Task 7/9
            </p>
            <!-- heading begins -->
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold">Mutate Network</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm my-5">
                We will now submit a request to the netowrk to allow the tic-tak-toe game access your data
                (including the one it writes) on the internet. 
            </p>
            <!-- subheading  -->
            <div class="pt-5">
                <div class="flex gap-3 items-center text-xs pb-4 text-gray-400 relative  group">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        style="fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);transform: msFilter" class="w-[12px] h-[12px]">
                        <path
                            d="M8.707 19.707 18 10.414 13.586 6l-9.293 9.293a1.003 1.003 0 0 0-.263.464L3 21l5.242-1.03c.176-.044.337-.135.465-.263zM21 7.414a2 2 0 0 0 0-2.828L19.414 3a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L15 4.586 19.414 9 21 7.414z">
                        </path>
                    </svg>
                    Make your decisions known and executed on the network.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col w-full border border-gray-100 p-6">
                <form action="" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div id="form-group">
                        <div class="group">
                            <label for="smDid" class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-2 block">SamaritanDB DID</label>
                            <input disabled type="text" name="samaritan_did" id="smDid"
                                placeholder="Enter your Samaritan DID"
                                class="form-input samaritan_did border border-gray-200 text-xs text-gray-500 w-full py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none">
                            <div
                                class="absolute text-sm invisible group-hover:visible w-48 p-2 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex gap-3">
                                ðŸ’¡ This is your SamaritanDB DID. It identifies you and your data across the internet.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="form-group">
                        <div class="group">
                            <label for="appDid" class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-2 block">Applcation's DID</label>
                            <input disabled type="text" name="application_did" id="appDid"
                                placeholder="Enter the application's DID"
                                value="did:sam:apps:5GWH4sLKB3NB3iKB8e4zcQmouoCbjwF9372Kgo7qgSYbwAGq"
                                class="form-input border border-gray-200 text-xs text-gray-500 w-full py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none">
                            <div
                                class="absolute text-sm invisible group-hover:visible w-48 p-2 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex gap-3">
                                ðŸ’¡ This is the DID of the Tic-Tac-Toe game. You'll submit it to the network as the
                                application in which you want to access your data (beacuse you denied it access
                                earlier).
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="form-group">
                        <label for="action" class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-2 block">Action</label>
                        <select id="action" name="action"
                            class="form-input w-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-500 p-2 rounded-md appearance-none focus:outline-none text-xs">
                            <option value="" selected disabled>Select an action</option>
                            <option disabled value="deny">Deny application access</option>
                            <option value="allow">Allow application access</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div id="form-group">
                        <div class="group">
                            <label for="privateKey" class="text-smm text-gray-800 mb-2 block">Private Key</label>
                            <input type="text" id="private-keys" name="private_key" disabled
                                value="dilemma quarter decrease simple climb boring liberty tobacco upper axis neutral suit"
                                class="form-input border border-gray-200 text-xs text-gray-500 w-full py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none">
                            <div
                                class="absolute invisible group-hover:visible w-[300px] p-2 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex gap-3">
                                ðŸ’¡ Your private keys ensure you are the one making the request and no one else. We use
                                our private keys here because your account is
                                not funded. In production, only you can make the changes.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="important-data hidden" data-next="8"
                        data-hint="Now that you've allowed the application access to your data across the internet, we will check the leaderboard again.">
                    </div>
                    <div class="group">
                        <button id="submit" onclick="return false"
                            class="justify-center flex gap-2 mutate-btn w-full transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out bg-black text-white border-none py-2 px-4 cursor-pointer my-5 text-sm">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="animate-spin h-[20px] w-[20px] stroke-white hidden" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                style="fill: #fff;">
                                <path
                                    d="M2 11h5v2H2zm15 0h5v2h-5zm-6 6h2v5h-2zm0-15h2v5h-2zM4.222 5.636l1.414-1.414 3.536 3.536-1.414 1.414zm15.556 12.728-1.414 1.414-3.536-3.536 1.414-1.414zm-12.02-3.536 1.414 1.414-3.536 3.536-1.414-1.414zm7.07-7.071 3.536-3.535 1.414 1.415-3.536 3.535z">
                                </path>
                            </svg>
                            <span>Submit Request</span>
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="absolute invisible group-hover:visible w-[300px] -m-7 p-2 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex gap-3">
                            ðŸ’¡ You will be submitting a transaction to the network to enforce your will across all
                            devices that are part of the network on the internet.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-300 text-center py-1 mt-10">
            Copyright &copy; 2023 Algorealm Inc. All Rights Reserved
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>